\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boldsymbol{u}_{i}=u_{i}^{\parallel}\hat{\mathbf{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}+\boldsymbol{u}_{i}^{\perp}\cdot(\boldsymbol{I}-\hat{\mathbf{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}\hat{\mathbf{\boldsymbol{\rho}}}).
\]

\end_inset

Defining the force due to the driving of the trap as 
\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{f}_{i}(t)=k_{i}\boldsymbol{u}_{i}^{0}(t)$
\end_inset

