 we obtain decoupled equations for motion for each component of motion.
 For motion along the trap, we obtain a pair of coupled ordinary differential
 equations
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\gamma_{ij}^{||}\dot{u}_{j}^{||}+k_{i}u_{i}^{||}=f_{i}^{||}(t).
\end{equation}

\end_inset


